ats?  Do you have a special workroom order form for curtains?</p>\n<p>Thank you!!!<br />\nHillary</p></div>\n<div class=\"clr\" style=\"clear: both;\"></div>\n</p></div>\n<div class=\"form_row\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px;\">\n<div class=\"input_label\" style=\"float: left; width: 30%; margin-right: 3%; font-weight: bold; text-align: right; margin-right: 15px; color: #111;\">Attachment</div>\n<div class=\"input_element\" style=\"float: left; width: 65%; font-weight: bold; color: #134b99; \">Please find the attachment.</div>\n<div class=\"clr\" style=\"clear: both;\"></div>\n</p></div>\n<div class=\"form_row\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px;\">\n<div class=\"input_label\" style=\"float: left; width: 30%; margin-right: 3%; font-weight: bold; text-align: right; margin-right: 15px; color: #111;\">Best Time to Call</div>\n<div class=\"input_element\" style=\"float: left; width: 65%; font-weight: bold; color: #134b99; \">anytime, but I work from 8-3pm MST every day.</div>\n<div class=\"clr\" style=\"clear: both;\"></div>\n</p></div>\n<div class=\"form_row\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px;\">\n<div class=\"input_label\" style=\"float: left; width: 30%; margin-right: 3%; font-weight: bold; text-align: right; margin-right: 15px; color: #111;\">Sofa/Chair</div>\n<div class=\"input_element\" style=\"float: left; width: 65%; font-weight: bold; color: #134b99; \">basically sofa 2</div>\n<div class=\"clr\" style=\"clear: both;\"></div>\n</p></div>\n<div class=\"form_row\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px; min-height: 20px;\">\n<div class=\"input_label\" style=\"float: left; width: 30%; margin-right: 3%; font-weight: bold; text-align: right; margin-right: 15px; color: #111;\">How do you hear?</div>\n<div class=\"input_element\" style=\"float: left; width: 65%; font-weight: bold; color: #134b99; \">Other</div>\n<div class=\"clr\" style=\"clear: both;\"></div>\n</p></div>\n</div>\n</body>\n</ht