ody</div>\r\n<div class=\"clr\" style=\"clear: both;\"></div>\r\n</p></div>\r\n<div class=\"form_row\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px;\">\r\n<div class=\"input_label\" style=\"float: left; width: 30%; margin-right: 3%; font-weight: bold; text-align: right; margin-right: 15px; color: #111;\">Email</div>\r\n<div class=\"input_element\" style=\"float: left; width: 65%; font-weight: bold; color: #134b99; \">elyse.moody@meredith.com</div>\r\n<div class=\"clr\" style=\"clear: both;\"></div>\r\n</p></div>\r\n<div class=\"form_row\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px;\">\r\n<div class=\"input_label\" style=\"float: left; width: 30%; margin-right: 3%; font-weight: bold; text-align: right; margin-right: 15px; color: #111;\">Subject</div>\r\n<div class=\"input_element\" style=\"float: left; width: 65%; font-weight: bold; color: #134b99; \">From Martha Stewart Living</div>\r\n<div class=\"clr\" style=\"clear: both;\"></div>\r\n</p></div>\r\n<div class=\"form_row\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px; min-height: 25px;\">\r\n<div class=\"input_label\" style=\"float: left; width: 30%; margin-right: 3%; font-weight: bold; text-align: right; margin-right: 15px; color: #111;\">Message</div>\r\n<div class=\"input_element\" style=\"float: left; width: 65%; font-weight: bold; color: #134b99; \">Hi there,</p>\r\n<p>I hope all is well, and happy holidays! I’m reaching out about the possibility of scheduling an interview in the next few weeks for a story I’m working on for Living’s April issue.</p>\r\n<p>We’re doing a feature on reupholstering furniture – my colleague Lorna Aragon, our home editor, suggested I reach out to you all because Luther does so much fine upholstery work for Martha. We think the timing is nice for Earth Day, because it&#039;s a sustainable choice, and love the creativity in the process too. Our story will walk readers through it, and help them make decisions that will make their piece even better than before. I’m hoping to get expert advice and tips on how to make smart choices.</p>\r\n<p>I know the holidays are a tricky time, so please let me know what sounds best for Luther, or another expert on your team if that&#039;s best. I’m hoping to have the story in on 1/6. I can be available anytime, and am happy to send questions over by email in case that’s easier.</p>\r\n<p>Thanks very much for your help!</p>\r\n<p>Best,<br />\r\nElyse</p>\r\n<p>Elyse Moody<br />\r\nSenior Editor<br />\r\nMartha Stewart Living<br />\r\n225 Liberty Street, 9th Fl.,<br />\r\nNew York, NY 10281<br />\r\n212.499.1983</p></div>\r\n<div class=\"clr\" style=\"clear: both;\"></div>\r\n</p></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>'),(10992,783,'original_headers','[]'),(10993,783,'session_transcript','smtp:none:none://mx10.mailspamprotection.com:587\n\n220 se16.mailspamprotection.com ESMTP Exim 20190913.1218 Wed, 18 Dec 2019 16:21:28 +0000\r\nEHLO lqustg.wpengine.com\r\n250-se16.mailspamprotection.com Hello 12.90.68.34.bc.googleusercontent.com [34.68.90.12]\r\n250-SIZE\r\n250-8BITMIME\r\n250-DSN\r\n250-AUTH PLAIN LOGIN\r\n250-STARTTLS\r\n250 HELP\r\nMAIL FROM:<info@lqu.com>\r\n250 OK\r\nRCPT TO:<quintana.luther@gmail.com>\r\n250 Accepted\r\nDATA\r\n354 Enter message, ending with \".\" on a line by itself\r\nX-Mailer: Postman SMTP 2.0.6 for WordPress (https://wordpress.org/plugins/post-smtp/)\r\nContent-Type: multipart/alternative;\r\n boundary=\"=_588387ad7eb4f460e400bee1e8223798\"\r\nFrom: \"Luther Quintana Upholstrry Inc.\" <info@lqu.com>\r\nSender: info@lqu.com\r\nTo: quintana.luther@gmail.com\r\nMessage-Id: <26b520165b4a2952098afc656d26bef4@lqupholstery.com>\r\nSubject: Contact Form Submission\r\nDate: Wed, 18 Dec 2019 16:21:28 +0000\r\nMIME-Version: 1.0\r\n\r\n--=_588387ad7eb4f460e400bee1e8223798\r\nContent-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\r\nContent-Transfer-Encoding: quoted-printable\r\n\r\nUser has submitted Contact Form. The detail of user form is as follow:=\r\n=0D=0A=0D=0A=0D=0AName=0D=0AEly